lank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BB%95-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-WDmPURbVLbTgQIPIWovNHg">Thuật cổ kỳ 2 - 述古其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem--LsKiQ1eOygSMk7fNhUr8w">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhị đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第二段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-pie5Fia6OX3GJydppNrLBw">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tứ đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第四段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/T%E1%BB%B1-qu%C3%A2n-chi-xu%E1%BA%A5t-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Ki-v7lij03FNOHEYWdxjbg">Tự quân chi xuất kỳ 2 - 自君之出矣其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-d0pAJju8J6ouE1xCNQH3eg">Trần Thúc Đạt</a>)<br></div>	</div>
